Package Model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Enemy
    This class is called in the constructor of GameLogic and is responsible of keeping track of all the enemy objects on the map.
    GameLogic
    This class is initiated when starting a new game and creates the logical structure of the map and its objects.
    ImageResources
    This class is used to return requested images or image-paths to view-objects.
    InteractiveObject
    This class is a superclass for item, enemy and player.
    Item
    This class is responsible for all the item objects in the game.
    Player
    This class is initiated in the constructor of GameLogic and is responsible of keeping track of all player related stats.
    SoundManager
    Used for reading sound files and playing them.
    Tile
    This class is created in GameLogic and is responsible for its position, image ID, if there is a collision and also if there is darkness on the map.
